messages.content: Hey! So you're a programmer, huh? That's so cool! How do you like it?
Hi! Yeah, I love it. I've been doing it for about a year now. How about you? Do you like journalism?
I really do. I write for a local news site, and it's an amazing job.
That's so cool. I'm glad you enjoy what you do. I think that's important.
lol so your profile says no man buns. What's the deal with that?
Haha omg, why, you don't have one do you?
No, just curious why you put it lol
Haha cuz they're so ridiculous! Like, I could not take a guy seriously who has a man bun
I'm into more manly guys.
I see. What's your definition of manly?
Hm, let's see...
I like a man who can take care of his woman, who has some good facial hair, who dresses well. You know, things like that.
What's your definition of ladylike?
Haha I don't know, I don't really have one. I'm into all different kinds of people.
Wait, you're originally from New Jersey? omg you're not a Giants fan are you?
No haha, why?
I just have to make sure lol. that's very important. I loooove my patriots!
yeah it seems like most people around here feel that way
are you not a patriots fan?
Nah, I'm not into football
whaaaat?? how can you not like football? what sports do you like then?
I've never really been into sports. I don't know why, they've just never interested me much. I do like being outside though, hiking, camping, stuff like that
ooo I love hiking too. do you like kayaking?
I love kayaking! I went recently on Cape Cod and it was so fun!
Would you want to go this weekend? I know this great spot for it
For sure! That sounds super fun
Great! I'll hit you up soon
Hey, how's it going?
Ugh, it's going. Been a long couple of days.
Oh, I'm sorry to hear that. Work stuff?
Nah, I've had to deal with my ex, getting back stuff from his apartment and whatnot
ah, I can imagine that's rough
Yeah, he's a dick haha. What about you? Any crazy exes?
Hm, not really. I tend to get along with most of exes. I haven't had many bad breakups.
Well, that's a good sign! When was your last relationship?
I think my last partner and I broke up around 6 months ago? Something like that.
And you still talk to her?
him, and yeah, we still talk
what do you mean him?
Oh, I mean my last partner was a man, not a woman
wait....you're gay???
no, I date women as well
but you also like guys?
yeah
I see
is that a problem...?
No! I mean, I have NO problem with gay people at all!
Well, I'm not gay. Like I said, I date women as well as men.
Right. and that's totally totally cool.
cool, that's a relief. i'm glad you're cool with it.
totally
So where is this place you want to go kayaking this weekend?
Hey, just wanted to check if we were still down for this weekend?
